421
01:11:49,520 --> 01:12:01,360
Sveža moja duša moja, moja posljednja i prva ljubav.

422
01:12:48,640 --> 01:12:54,400
U noć povedi me, uzmi me i ljubi me.

423
01:12:56,000 --> 01:13:01,760
I s ovog ludog snaga nikad ne probudi me.

424
01:13:03,680 --> 01:13:09,760
Sate živim ja, sad te umreću.

425
01:13:11,840 --> 01:13:15,680
I sve dok živim o tebi, pjevaču.
